title: Ep. - 302 - DAVID AND ANNIE FROM 90 DAY FIANCE AMANDA HIRSCH REVIEWS THE BACHELORETTE
description:
David and Annie from 90 Day Fiance and Pillow Talk talk about their new digital series cooking Thai-inspired meals, and what it is like having the tables turned on them having to review other 90 Day Fiance couples on Pillow Talk.

 

Amanda Hirsch, host of Not Skinny But Not Fat podcast, reviews the absurdity of this season of The Bachelorette.
